## Phase I — AI Governance Foundation
**Status: Complete**

The foundational governance architecture. Delivered to the Cloud Security Alliance and currently under enterprise expansion. Established the STAR CAR-D 20-domain compliance framework, OPA/Rego policy enforcement layer, and immutable audit logging infrastructure that all subsequent phases build on.

**Key Deliverables:**
- STAR CAR-D 20-domain AI compliance framework
- OPA/Rego policy enforcement engine
- Immutable tamper-evident audit log pipeline
- CSA STAR for AI Working Group contribution (~80% of compliance-layer development)
- GEN-SHIELD DevSecOps pipeline
- cATO (Continuous Authorization to Operate) — reducing ATO timelines from months to days

